FUNGAL MENINGITIS - MEXICO (02): (DURANGO) FATAL, CONTAMINATED EPIDURAL ANESTHETIC SUSPECTED, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
*********************************************************************************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

Date: Tue 27 Dec 2022 14:06 EST
Source: Yahoo [in Spanish, machine trans., abridged, edited]
https://es-us.noticias.yahoo.com/reportan-fallecimiento-brote-meningitis-durango-190646813.html


The number of patients who have died from the meningitis outbreak in that entity has risen to 29, according to the Durango Health Secretariat, since one of the 3 patients who were transferred to Mexico City to receive care at the National Institute of Neurology and Neurosurgery died on Monday [26 Dec 2022]. 77 confirmed cases of meningitis, 74 women and 3 men, have been reported as well as 26 hospital discharges.

On Tuesday [27 Dec 2022], the deputy medical director of the General Hospital 450, where all the patients with meningitis have been concentrated, Hugo Almonte de León, reported that one of the patients transferred to the National Institute of Neurology and Neurosurgery, in Mexico City, showed improvement and [was] returned to the medical unit in Durango.

For his part, David Payán, coordinator of Special Care for Victims and Relatives of Meningitis in Durango, said that 574 protocol medical evaluations of meningitis have been granted, 265 supports in diapers and milk, 246 for free transportation, and 493 psychological interventions for patients and relatives. In addition, he explained that the state government has provided 23 funeral aids and 2800 food rations, and 129 various efforts, and that the accompaniment to the relatives of the patients will continue until the end of the health emergency.

The Durango Secretariat explained that 1800 people continue to be observed, who are undergoing diagnostic tests to provide early care if they require it.

